<p>It's equivalent to</p>

<pre><code>while (x-- &gt; 0)
</code></pre>

<p><code>x--</code> (post decrement) is equivalent to <code>x = x-1</code> so, the code transforms to:</p>

<pre><code>while(x &gt; 0) {
    x = x-1;
    // logic
}
x--;   // The post decrement done when x &lt;= 0
</code></pre>
